Package com.atakmap.map.elevation.quadtree

Changed Classes
ElevationNode This object represents a node in the ElevationQuadTree which can store data for for the elevation based on the area that it covers.
ElevationQuadTree This object represents a quad tree implementation that allows the storage of elevation data in grid aligned nodes where lower nodes can provide more detailed grid representations.
NodeElevationData This object is used to store the elevation data for a given quad tree node
QuadTreeElevationTerrain This is the implementation of the GLTerrain which uses a quad tree for storage and lookup of the elevation data.
